metadata.name: Leeloo
metadata.description:
I took a picture of my wife, in Etel (France)  
It was a beautiful July afternoon and I decided to take this picture.  
It's a creation that I love because it wasn't my first idea for the position, but my wife took the liberty and it works better, she's amazing.
